snippet.title: Celebs React To Johnny Depp Winning $7 Million Settlement Against Amber!
snippet.description:
Celebrities React To Johnny Depp Winning The $7 Million Settlement Against Amber Heard!

✅ Like & Subscribe for more Celebrity Content!

Things are finally looking good for Johnny Depp in the current dispute against Amber Heard, as the Judge sides in favor of the Pirates of the Caribbean actor. She now has to prove to the court that she did in fact donate the $7 Million from her divorce settlement with Johnny Depp by showing sufficient documentation. In response, many celebrities reacted to this headline, both friends close to Johnny and also relatives like his daughter Lily-Rose Depp. But what triggered this change? And what did these other celebs and relatives have to say?

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard #Sia
